      <title>欧洲钢铁制造商在德国支出上激增，中国产出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/european-steelmakers-surge-on-german-spending-china-output-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲钢铁制造商在德国承诺放松其钱包弦并提高基础设施和防御上的支出后，扩大了一场陡峭的公牛，而中国则承诺减少其钢铁产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/european-steelmakers-surge-on-german-spending-china-output-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 16:00:33 GMT</pubDate>
