    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯的石油税收收入下降了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/russia-s-oil-tax-revenue-sinks-in-sign-production-is-falling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯2月份的石油税收收入遭受了近四分之一的同比的低迷，这表明生产商在征税项目中的产出中已经结束了，以满足该国的欧佩克+配额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/russia-s-oil-tax-revenue-sinks-in-sign-production-is-falling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 15:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
